    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a dream. I've taken great care of it, and it's just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin, I know you'll love it as much as I do!",
      "price": 29500.0,
