    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and the double-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the chassis remains taut; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates, and the rod bearings have been serviced\u2014crucial preventative maintenance for this platform. The suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, utilizing McPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for telepathic handling. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and interior bolster wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the drivetrain maintains excellent compression and thermal efficiency.",
      "price": 31500.0,
