    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i Sedan is a refined blend of executive luxury and athletic performance, finished in a timeless Deep Sea Blue Metallic. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Mocha Dakota leather and Fineline Ridge wood trim. The upholstery is supple and smoke-free, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the heated seats and ambient lighting to the intuitive iDrive infotainment system, operates as intended. Under the hood, the 3.0L inline-six engine runs flawlessly, benefiting from a documented service history and a recent oil and filter change. The tires show plenty of remaining tread, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, reliable, and meticulously maintained vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
